name: Tricking #2
description:
Tricking - a training discipline that combines kicks with flips and twists from martial arts and gymnastics as well as many dance moves and styles from breakdancing.

Back Full - a backflip with a full twist. The performer jumps up and rotates 360 degrees along the sagittal plane (or about the x-axis) while at the same time spinning 360 degrees along the transverse plane, before returning to his feet.
